svg.title: LITA
svg.desc: LITA.co is the participative investment platform dedicated to social entrepreneurship and sustainable development. Created in January 2014 by Eva Sadoun and Julien Benayoun, LITA.co, formerly 1001PACT, collected 7 million euros from 2,000 individuals to finance 24 social enterprises.
